body:
Hi,
I‘m using the release version of verilator-4.202 and here is my example:


```verilog
module top(clk);
	input clk;
	logic [15:0] index;
	logic [15:0] data;
	logic [15:0] mem[7:0];

	always @(posedge clk)
		begin
			data  <= data + 1'b1;
			index <= index + 1'b1;
			mem[index] <= data;  // index will be out of range
		end
endmodule
````

I notice that the verilator output cpp is as follows:
```c++    
VL_INLINE_OPT void Vtop::_sequent__TOP__3(Vtop__Syms* __restrict vlSymsp) {
    VL_DEBUG_IF(VL_DBG_MSGF("+    Vtop::_sequent__TOP__3\n"); );
    Vtop* const __restrict vlTOPp VL_ATTR_UNUSED = vlSymsp->TOPp;
    // Variables
    // Begin mtask footprint all: 
    CData/*2:0*/ __Vdlyvdim0__top__DOT__mem__v0;
    SData/*15:0*/ __Vdly__top__DOT__data;
    SData/*15:0*/ __Vdly__top__DOT__index;
    SData/*15:0*/ __Vdlyvval__top__DOT__mem__v0;
    // Body
    __Vdly__top__DOT__index = vlTOPp->top__DOT__index;
    __Vdly__top__DOT__data = vlTOPp->top__DOT__data;
    __Vdly__top__DOT__data = (0xffffU & ((IData)(1U) 
                                         + (IData)(vlTOPp->top__DOT__data)));
    __Vdly__top__DOT__index = (0xffffU & ((IData)(1U) 
                                          + (IData)(vlTOPp->top__DOT__index)));
    __Vdlyvval__top__DOT__mem__v0 = vlTOPp->top__DOT__data;
    __Vdlyvdim0__top__DOT__mem__v0 = (7U & (IData)(vlTOPp->top__DOT__index));
    vlTOPp->top__DOT__data = __Vdly__top__DOT__data;
    vlTOPp->top__DOT__index = __Vdly__top__DOT__index;
    vlTOPp->top__DOT__mem[__Vdlyvdim0__top__DOT__mem__v0] 
        = __Vdlyvval__top__DOT__mem__v0;
}
```

this code `__Vdlyvdim0__top__DOT__mem__v0 = (7U & (IData)(vlTOPp->top__DOT__index));` shows that only the lower 3-bit used as the index.
If the index exceeds the depth of the array, will incorrectly assigned to the array.
In VCS simulation, indexes that exceed the array depth are ignored and no value is assigned.

Can you solve this problem by keeping the simulation behavior of the verilator consistent with that of the VCS?
